item.title: Teleport Command?
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

Assuming the source is DeltaScape:

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("name")) { toX = int; toY = int; sM("Message."); }

If not:

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("name")) { teleportToX = int; teleportToY = int; sendMessage("Message."); }
